response_text: I couldn’t locate the exact URL for the Pushbullet pricing page. I recommend visiting their [official website](https://www.pushbullet.com) and navigating to the relevant pricing or Pro information section.

extracted_content.content:
![Image 1](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/SMS.png)![Image 2](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/hover/SMS.png)

Android only

Send text messages

Typing on a keyboard is so much faster than typing on a phone. Easily send and receive texts on your computer.

![Image 3](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/notifications.png)![Image 4](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/hover/notifications.png)

iPhone only works with Mac, Android works with any Computer

See your phone's notifications

Never miss a call or a text again while working at your computer. Pushbullet shows you WhatsApp messages, texts, phone calls, and more.

![Image 5](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/channels.png)![Image 6](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/hover/channels.png)

Follow interesting things

Get notified about things you care about. A new xkcd post, new free games from EA, Google acquisitions, and more.

![Image 7](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/links.png)![Image 8](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/hover/links.png)

Send links

Instantly share links between any of your devices. Never email yourself a link again just to get it somewhere else.

![Image 9](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/chat.png)![Image 10](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/hover/chat.png)

Chat with friends

Pushbullet works great on all of your devices, which makes sharing and chatting with friends more convenient than ever.

![Image 11](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/files.png)![Image 12](https://www.pushbullet.com/img/landingpage/hover/files.png)

Send files

Moving pictures and files between your devices has never been easier. Files download automatically and can be opened right from the notifications.

pricing_data.pricing_notes: Pushbullet offers a free tier with basic functionality and a subscription-based Pro tier for advanced features.
